lead_paragraph: Allie Long scored her first two international goals, and the United States routed Colombia 7-0 Wednesday night in the Americans' first exhibition since five players filed a wage-discrimination action against the U.S. Soccer Federation.

headline.print_headline: Long Scores 1st 2 Goals as US Women Rout Colombia 7-0
